Creates a CLI command using buildCommand from @stricli/core that accepts a lineEnding flag with enum values ('lf' or 'crlf'). The command writes output to stdout indicating which line ending was selected. The flag has a default value of 'lf' and includes documentation for CLI help text.

```typescript
